ween the two)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;We can encourage everyone to stop by so we can multiply the giving! Over the past years we have raised over $9,000 together.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Thanks, everyone!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Participating blogs/Twitter handles:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://howdidmykarmaranovermydogma.blogspot.com/" target="_blank"&gt;My Karma Ran Over My Dogma&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
