/" target="_blank"&gt;GigaOM&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://lunch.publishersmarketplace.com/2014/11/amazon-hachette-finalize-new-contract/" target="_blank"&gt;Publishers Lunch&lt;/a&gt; (subscription required)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.vox.com/2014/10/22/7016827/amazon-hachette-monopoly" target="_blank"&gt;Vox&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;My sources tell me that we haven't read the last blog post about how traditional publishers are the guardians of truth and Amazon is the root of all evil or that traditional publishers are antiquarian luddites and Amazon is saving the world for readers.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Stand by...&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: x-small;"&gt;Art: Club Night by George Bellows&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
